## What's the story Mother

You are the crew on a routine colonist transfer mission from Heske 337 to Sol.
The colonists are part of a UA WY sponsored mission are will remain in cyrosleep for the duration
including the loading and offloading at Africa Station, Earth.

The ship is the USCSS Simurgh a Bison Class freighter attached by umbilical to a colonial transporter. The
colonial transporter has 50 colonists in cyrosleep. As long as cyro is active, in an emergency the transporter
can eject the pods straight into space and activate an emergency transponder.
